name: Replicard LAD
text: You can banish 1 other Level 7 or higher monster from your hand; Special Summon this card from your hand. You can target 1 face-up monster you control; Special Summon 1 monster from your Deck with a different name that has 2 or more of the same Level, ATK, and/or DEF, but it cannot activate its effects this turn. You can only use each effect of "Replicard LAD" once per turn.
